data.description: FREE one year home warranty, courtesy of the seller! FLOOD ZONE X -- no mandatory flood insurance! Adorable home on an oversized, corner lot with western exposure for beautiful Southwest Florida sunsets! No known damage from hurricane Ian! Seller has given the exterior charming updates including a fresh coat of paint, a new fence around the large backyard, and an additional paved patio! Inside, you find an open concept, new luxury, vinyl plank flooring in the bedrooms, new white shaker-style cabinets and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. This is a wonderful opportunity for a family and/or pet-owners to truly utilize the large lawn! You're never far from everything Cape Coral has to offer, as it's situated in the Pelican area -- just minutes from the restaurants and businesses of the South Cape Entertainment District and also from Veterans Parkway. It's only a four minute drive to the closest grocery story and about a 10 minute drive from Cape Coral's only beach. The fenced yard has double gates on both sides, large enough to drive through if needed. All city utilities are in and assessments are paid!
